description: The investment seeks to track the price and yield performance, before fees and expenses, of the prices used by the EuroMTS Broad Investment Grade 5-7 index. The index is a composition of bonds that issued by the goverments of member states of the euro zone with a maturity between 5 and 7 years with at least two notations in the investment grade category in the rating agencies S&P, Moody's and Fitch.
name: Amundi ETF Govt Bond EuroMTS Broad Investment Grade 5-7 UCITS ETF DR C
